OL,3,CITV annual profits drop amid 'severe
OL,4,Cdecline' in advertising
OL,6,FITV said its profits dropped last year
OL,7,Fas the broadcaster found it
OL,8,F"challenging" to encourage advertisers
OL,9,Fto spend money on traditional TV
OL,10,Fcommercials.
OL,12,FThe company behind Love Island
OL,13,Freported growth at some of its
OL,14,Fbusiness units, but it proved a
OL,15,Fstruggle to keep its advertising take
OL,16,Fup.
OL,18,FProfit fell from #501 million in 2022
OL,19,Fto #193 million before tax last year,
OL,20,FITV said.
