OL,3,CITV annual profits drop amid 'severe
OL,4,Cdecline' in advertising
OL,6,FIt was what the business calls
OL,7,F"linear" advertising ` the industry's
OL,8,Fword for the ads shown on television
OL,9,Frather than online ` which really
OL,10,Fstruggled.
OL,12,FITV said it had seen a "severe
OL,13,Fdecline" of 15% in linear advertising,
OL,14,Fas companies that normally advertise
OL,15,Fwere more cautious because of the poor
OL,16,Fglobal economy.
OL,18,FHowever, digital revenue performed
OL,19,Fmuch better, increasing 19% to #490
OL,20,Fmillion.
