OL,3,CITV annual profits drop amid 'severe
OL,4,Cdecline' in advertising
OL,6,FReduced advertising spending is also
OL,7,Fhitting international broadcasters,
OL,8,Fmeaning they have less money to spend
OL,9,Fon TV programmes from ITV Studios, the
OL,10,Fcompany said.
OL,12,FITV told investors on Thursday: "2024
OL,13,Fwill be impacted by the 2023 US
OL,14,Fwriters' and actors' strikes, which
OL,15,Fwill delay around #80 million of
OL,16,Frevenue from 2024 to 2025, as well as
OL,17,Fweaker demand from free-to-air
OL,18,Fbroadcasters in Europe who are holding
OL,19,Fback spend until they see more
OL,20,Fcertainty in the advertising market."
