OL,6,FBut that will come off the back of a
OL,7,Frecord year for ITV Studios' profit
OL,8,Fand revenue, as it produced hit shows
OL,9,Fincluding Love Island, a format which
OL,10,Fhas now been sold to 27 countries, and
OL,11,FMr Bates vs The Post Office, which was
OL,12,FITV's biggest new drama for more than
OL,13,F10 years.
OL,15,FChief Executive Dame Carolyn McCall
OL,16,Fsaid: "In 2023 we saw the benefit of
OL,17,Fthe actions we have taken to
OL,18,Freposition ITV towards higher
OL,19,Fsustainable growth.
